Which screws are you looking for? The assembly manual for the ball shifter has the callouts for the ones listed in the ball shifter pneumatic kit.

Looks like the following:
4-40 x 5/16 socket heads (fastens piston coupler)
6-32 x 1/4" button heads (mounts pancake cylinder)
8-32 x 1/2" button heads (mounts bracket to standoffs and standoffs to housing)
